<plot>This documentary details the case that the 1989 invasion of Panama by the US was motivated not by the need to protect American soldiers, restore democracy or even capture Noriega. It was to force Panama to submit the will of the United States after Noriega had exhausted his usefulness.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?581290</url></doc>
